  "description_text": "Invacare Platinum 9 Oxygen Concentrator\n\nInvacare Platinum 9 is a high-flow home oxygen concentrator that delivers an oxygen flow rate of 1-9 LPM at an oxygen purity level of 90-96% across all flow rates.\n\nWeight: Invacare Platinum 9 weighs 24.4 kgs. \n\nSound: The machine producers sound at 58 decibels.\n\nPower: Invacare Platinum 9 consumes 585 watts of power and has one of the lowest power consumption rates among high flow oxygen concentrators.\n\nOutlet Pressure: This device gives an outlet pressure of 28.5 psi, once again beating all the high-flow oxygen concentrators.\n\nAlarms: Loss of power, system malfunction and low flow oxygen alarm\n\nWarranty: Invacare Platinum 9 has a warranty period of 1 year.",
